<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,1440,2005]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[197,313,1476,1501]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41">Variation.</emphasis>
The height of the posterior carina of mesoscutellum is not constant, about 
<number box="[1165,1250,1476,1500]" pageId="5" pageNumber="41" value="0.8500000000000001" valueMax="1.3" valueMin="0.4">0.4–1.3</number>
